{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回海上惊魂。陆小凤登上老狐狸的海船，发现牛肉汤已在船上担任厨娘，船上八间上等舱房全有贵客入住。陆小凤对神秘同行者岳洋心生好奇，岳洋衣着考究、出手阔绰却冷酷异常。深夜，岳洋将陆小凤打落海中，却抛下救生小艇和银两。陆小凤在海上漂泊一夜，老狐狸的船因缺水返回，陆小凤得以重新上船。岸边发现神秘人物胡生的尸体，其轻功绝顶却离奇溺亡。陆小凤与牛肉汤在简陋澡堂相逢，关系暧昧。三日后突遭暴风雨，海船被打碎，岳洋在沉船前说出他早已知道此船会沉的真相。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "起锚！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扬帆！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "顺风！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你怎么会上船来的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你们上船来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我们上了船，你就要上船了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我问你，你们在船上，是不是也一样要吃饭？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我就是煮饭的，不但烧饭，还煮牛肉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你什么时候改行的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我本来就是烧饭的，只不过偶尔改行做做别的事而已！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说乘坐这条船的，都是很有身份的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这点我倒能想得到，否则怎么付得起老狐狸的船钱。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你有没有身份？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你只有钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "也没有，付了船钱后，我就已几乎完全破产。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "没有钱也没关系，如果你偶尔又吃错了药，我还是可以偶尔再改一次行的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这间房就是你的，只吃鸡蛋的那个混蛋住在右面第一间。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我能不能换一间？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不能！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为别的房里都已住着人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "那老狐狸劝我把这条船包下来，可是现在每间房里都有人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不但这里八间房全都有人，下面十六间也全都有人，老狐狸一向喜欢热闹，人越多他越高兴。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只不过住在这上面的才是贵客，老狐狸还特地叫我为你们烧几样好菜，今天晚上你想吃什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我想吃烤狐狸，烤得骨头都酥了的老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我外婆常说，要得到男人的心，就得先打通他的肠胃，只有会烧一手好菜的女人，才能嫁得到好丈夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们到处找你，你一个人溜到这里来干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "我受不了牛肉汤做的那些菜，想来钓几条鱼下酒。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你钓到几条？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "鱼虽然没钓着，却钓着条老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "你们明明已出海，又回来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我也是回来钓鱼的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "那边海上没有鱼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那边虽然也有鱼，却没有一条肯付我五百两船钱的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "我这条鱼也不肯付的，我上次已经付过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "上次是上次，这次是这次，上次是你自己要走的，我又没有把你推下去，所以这次若是还想上船，就得再付我五百两！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "你这人的心究竟有多黑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只不过比你钓起来的那条狐狸黑一点。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你好！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "你是不是在奇怪，我们为什么又回来了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "我们回来找你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么找我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "因为你要运的那批货太重，我们怕翻船，只有回来退给你！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "货不是我的，船也不是你的，这件事跟你和我都没有关系，你找我干什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "如果货不是你的，你是到这里来干什么的？特地来用鸡鸣五更返魂香对付你的兄弟？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "奇怪吧？我们居然又碰面了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我奇怪的只不过是连十个蛋你都吃不完。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "所以你下次若还想打我落水时，最好记住一件事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "我不喜欢吃白水煮蛋，我喜欢黄酒牛肉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "下次你再落水时，恐怕已只有一样东西可吃。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你自己的肉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "想不到你这人还满喜欢干净的，居然还会自己来洗澡。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "不自己来洗，难道还去找个人抱着洗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是不是为了想偷看我洗澡，才来洗澡的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "喜欢偷看别人洗澡的，好像并不是我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我可以偷看你，你可不能偷看我——",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你实在不是好东西。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
